name: Alla
description: Most of all I like to ride a bike, sing and cook tasty things. I like to take care about my close people and my friends. Character I am a down to earth, romantic person, with a sense of humor, good heart and a clear understanding of what I value in my life and what I want. I am a cheerful, kind, loyal, caring lady, who is able to love and wanting to be loved. I prefer a romantic dinner with my loved one at home instead of a noisy party in the company of many people…
